{
  "refrain": {
    "lines": [
      {
        "number": 1,
        "text": "Faith is the victory!"
      },
      {
        "number": 2,
        "text": "Faith is the victory!"
      },
      {
        "number": 3,
        "text": "Oh, glorious victory"
      },
      {
        "number": 4,
        "text": "That overcomes the world."
      }
    ]
  },
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Encamped along the hills of light,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Ye Christian soldiers, rise,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "And press the battle ere the night"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Shall veil the glowing skies."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Against the foe in vales below,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Let all our strength be hurled;"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Faith is the victory, we know,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "That overcomes the world."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "His banner over us in love,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Our sword the Word of God;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "We tread the road the saints above"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "With shouts of triumph trod."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "By faith they, like whirlwind’s breath,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Swept on o’er ev’ry field;"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "The faith by which they conquered death"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "Is still our shining shield."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "To him who overcomes the foe"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "White raiment shall be giv’n;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Before the angels he shall know"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "His name confessed in heav’n."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Then onward from the hills of light,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Our hearts with love aflame;"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "We’ll vanquish all the hosts of night,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "In Jesus’ conq’ring name."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    }
  ],
  "title": "Faith Is the Victory"
}
